snippet.title: Don't Stare - Teaser (2020)
snippet.description:
Escape overly-friendly talkative strangers with impressive feats of parkour in Don't Stare.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/14...

About Ascended Studio:
Escape from reality! We encourage this form of “delusion” because we understand that there are people out there who really want to be in another reality. We understand we can’t exactly be some superhero that changes the whole universe - but we can be something positive.

Follow Don't Stare for the latest updates:
» Discord: https://discord.gg/wXjtfDY
» Twitter: https://twitter.com/DontStareGame
» Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dontstaregame/
» Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/dont_stare_game

#DontStare #AscendedStudio #Unity
